Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:19.44,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:25.26,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,a thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:31.01,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.22,0:00:37.21,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,the Light struck
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:43.28,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:49.02,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:53.13,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,and fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:58.23,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\Nas the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:01.49,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.73,0:01:06.86,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:12.88,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,That blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:18.37,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:24.50,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:51.04,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(93,137)}Farewell to Tenderness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:01:58.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:13.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't decided, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:15.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:21.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But why? If you quit the military, I wouldn't\Ncare if I quit being a singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.93,0:02:24.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say something like that so lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:28.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no reason for you to go on killing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:31.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as if I do it because I enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:36.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I still remember
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:38.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,the way we were when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:45.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't a soldier yet and I was just\Nan ordinary girl, not a singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:51.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When we were trapped onboard the Macross\Nand we thought we were going to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:54.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,that's when you asked me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:05.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"What do you say we have\Na wedding ceremony?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:10.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to how things used to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:13.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:39.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Reaction core status?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:43.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Reaction core connections are nominal.\NEnergy levels are increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:45.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it, Kamujin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:46.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.59,0:03:49.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we can run wild again,\Njust like the old days!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:50.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We start with the Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:52.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we've smashed it, we'll\Nhead back into space!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:54.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:40.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where you've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:42.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking all over for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:46.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander-in-Chief Global wants to\Nsee you on the old bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:49.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Commander-in-Chief? On the old bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:51.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:53.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:05:01.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Claudia, thank you for everything, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:04.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're going to resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:08.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go doing something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:11.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Or don't you care if Minmay\Nsteals him away from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:14.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:18.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, as a woman, even I have to\Nadmit that Minmay is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:20.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And how do I compare?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:23.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm older than Ichijo, I'm uptight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:26.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm a soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:28.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why you're resigning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:32.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bear to stay in the military,\Nhaving to see him every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:34.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:46.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Major Hayase reporting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:47.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:50.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's just as it was\Nback then, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? That it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:57.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk to you about\Nyour new assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:06:00.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,New assignment? But Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:07.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Commander-in-Chief.\NBeing here brings back some old habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:09.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Hayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:12.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I want YOU to be the captain\Nof a ship of your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:16.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be captaining a ship that's\Nbeing constructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:18.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? A captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:20.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll accept, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:28.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Commander, but I'm thinking\Nof quitting the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.12,0:06:31.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a bit drastic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.51,0:06:33.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Ichijo is the cause of this, I assume?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:35.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:41.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When a female officer suddenly wants\Nto quit, that's always the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:53.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this scenery, Hayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:03.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:08.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Earth is truly a beautiful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:09.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:14.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't stay on this world forever, Hayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:20.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Out there in that vast galaxy the Zentradi\Nand the Supervision Army
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:22.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,are at this very moment locked in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:25.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If they come to attack the Earth again,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:29.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,our chances of survival are\Nless than one in a million.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:32.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you captured the Factory Satellite
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:34.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and have been strengthening\Nour battle readiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:36.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:42.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But consider: If we had the military\Nmight to resist such an armada,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:45.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,the Earth would become a world\Nthat existed only for warfare,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:48.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,just like the once-great Protoculture
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:54.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,who in creating their giant Zentradi\Nsoldiers destroyed themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:03.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want us to spread out to the stars, so that\NEarth's culture will never disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:04.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Space emigration?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:10.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, as quickly as possible and to\Nas many planets as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:12.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:33.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we'll be able to reach the\NMacross without being detected!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:34.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:44.22,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"If you quit the military, I wouldn't\Ncare if I quit being a singer."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:52.36,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"There's no reason for you to go on killing!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:57.37,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's go back to how things used to be!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:09:00.67,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's go back... to how things used to be."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:04.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:05.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:08.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:09.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Hayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:11.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Ichijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:16.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:23.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd planned to quit the military today\Nand go someplace far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:28.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But I changed my mind when I was picked\Nto take command of the first ship
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:30.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,in the Space Emigration Project.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:31.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Space emigration?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:37.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, even if humanity is able\Nto live here indefinitely,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:41.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,the Earth could one day very well\Nbe destroyed by aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:44.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of the children yet to be born,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:48.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,to preserve our culture for others\Nthousands of years in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:54.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe we need to fly out to\Nevery planet in the galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:59.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But not to kill: to spread culture\Namong the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:02.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:07.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Minmay, I love your songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:13.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't create culture the way you can
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:15.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but I might be able to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:16.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Hayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:23.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... Right now, I can come\Nright out and say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:27.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:30.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:33.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of your songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:41.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:55.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,M... Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:57.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:10:59.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:03.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:06.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:13.85,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:21.07,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:24.75,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:36.90,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Major! Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.79,0:11:38.75,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:43.81,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:49.09,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.69,0:11:50.37,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:51.64,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.04,0:11:53.14,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:55.31,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,An attack, a large-scale one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:58.16,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't we spot them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:02.96,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but they're\Ngoing all out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:05.49,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to the Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:10.25,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Major Hayase! I'm going out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:11.79,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:14.96,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:21.21,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:25.61,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.13,0:12:26.06,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:28.19,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to keep fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:39.90,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay, who is it that you sing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:45.65,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,For yourself? Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:51.98,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not for the people who love your songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:03.20,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We fight for the same reason\Nthat you sing your songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:05.04,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:07.56,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! You need to get to a shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:09.84,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No! If I'm going to evacuate,\Nyou're coming too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:11.65,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:15.72,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a soldier! I have to\Nprotect you... and the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:20.11,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! Then take me with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:22.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:27.32,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay, I'm sorry. But you're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:32.57,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go. You have your songs, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:49.13,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:53.00,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru... Hikaru... Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.57,0:13:55.27,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:13:58.69,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the enemy's status?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:01.77,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,One gunboat, closing in at high speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.97,0:14:05.04,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Range: 50 km at one o'clock. Altitude: 300.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:05.78,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:14.88,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy ship has entered the\Nmain cannon's line of fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:17.53,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! All hands, prepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:20.71,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,After the main cannon has fired,\Nlaunch all aerial battle pods!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:26.82,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy ship has entered the F Line\Nand is still closing in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:31.84,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm picking up a high-level energy\Nsignature that's building quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:32.62,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:33.87,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's headed straight for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:04.72,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma... Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:15.30,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Major! Respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:17.65,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Major! Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:19.11,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Major Hayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:25.00,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:41.60,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sub-systems 1 and 2 are not responding!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.16,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.26,0:15:46.66,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not getting anything either.\NAll control systems are offline.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:48.85,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Major?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:50.61,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, the Macross will...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:54.26,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Just like old times, isn't it, Captain?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.01,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:15:58.85,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:15.40,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What took you all so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:16.67,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Claudia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:18.23,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:20.37,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Man your stations at once, people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:21.71,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:22.88,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:25.84,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're launching the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:28.55,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So it can still fly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:31.18,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but not for very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:31.98,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:31.98,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:36.24,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All hands, stand by for launch.\NFire the main cannon at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:39.01,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take them out with one blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:40.23,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.72,0:16:45.88,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Auxiliary reaction-core output is climbing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:48.64,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All personnel, brace for liftoff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:52.88,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Gravity control systems are nominal.\NFive seconds to launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:55.32,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Three, two, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:56.59,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:08.45,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:12.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Macross! The Macross is lifting off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:28.64,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Macross...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:30.45,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Macross is flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:35.89,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:40.80,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,a thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:42.16,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Output in the main cannon's firing\Nsystem is still climbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:43.19,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,One minute to firing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:46.59,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:46.62,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention, all pilots engaged in combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:49.19,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Macross is preparing to\Nfire its main cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:53.86,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,the Light struck
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:52.18,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Get clear of the enemy ship at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:59.39,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:05.09,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:05.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat, get clear of the enemy ship at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:07.60,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Major?! You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:10.19,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,and fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:10.59,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Now firing the main cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:14.95,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\Nas the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:12.94,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Get clear of the enemy ship now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:15.69,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:18.43,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:17.65,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.62,0:18:23.80,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:19.94,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:30.07,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,That blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:28.06,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:34.99,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:41.23,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:50.18,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Oigur, we'll plow straight into them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.72,0:18:51.52,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oigur!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:56.56,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Let's do it, Lap'Lamiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:18:58.82,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Don't die, Kamujin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:02.62,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Same to you. We'll do some\Nculture afterwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:10.07,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:20.81,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, the enemy ship's not changing\Ncourse! It's going to ram us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:23.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Are they crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:26.20,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All batteries, open fire!\NDrive off the enemy ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:28.96,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Auxiliary reaction core has failed!\NThe Macross is inoperative!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:31.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy distance: 300 meters!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:32.68,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're unable to evade!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:36.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,MISA!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:57.05,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lap'Lamiz!\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Kamujin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:47.78,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all right, Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:49.89,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you. Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:53.01,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Minmay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:21:00.34,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go to a city\NI've never been to before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:05.25,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I'm there, I'll try singing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.23,0:21:08.56,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never think about giving up singing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:12.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds good, Minmay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:16.43,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Hayase?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:20.63,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know when this might be,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:26.37,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but when I'm finally able to sing my\Ntrue songs, when that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:27.93,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.02,0:21:32.15,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you let me come onboard your ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.30,0:21:33.93,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be glad to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:38.50,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll let your songs echo\Nthrough the galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.39,0:21:45.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.59,0:21:54.72,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, take care, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:21:57.35,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Minmay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:06.97,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd better get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.11,0:22:12.47,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.04,0:22:35.53,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.96,0:22:39.59,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you want to try to\Nkeep her from leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.71,0:22:44.52,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, a girl like Minmay can't get\Ntied down to a guy like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.56,0:22:45.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.39,0:22:50.50,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, can't you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.28,0:22:52.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay's song...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.21,0:23:01.62,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,I took your tenderness for granted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.40,0:22:53.76,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Her song?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.72,0:23:07.72,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to try to shine someday
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.53,0:23:05.49,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I can hear it, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:13.70,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,So for now, farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.43,0:23:52.73,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose it anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.85,0:23:59.07,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,My own path that I'm walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.89,0:24:06.06,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,We all keep running to the end
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.15,0:24:13.60,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still are far from the goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.67,0:24:19.89,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,In the days that leave behind today,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.27,0:24:25.84,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be glad when comes tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.45,0:24:33.51,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.60,0:24:44.39,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,The light that shines so far away
